OL,3,CArena survivor hopes to protect
OL,4,Cdaughter from 'stalker man' conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheorist
OL,7,FA Manchester Arena bombing survivor
OL,8,Fsays he is taking landmark legal
OL,9,Faction against a conspiracy theorist
OL,10,Fto save his daughter from "the stalker
OL,11,Fman".
OL,13,FMartin and Eve Hibbert, suffered life-
OL,14,Fchanging injuries after attending the
OL,15,FAriana Grande concert in May 2017.
OL,17,FMr Hibbert was left with a spinal cord
OL,18,Finjury, while Miss Hibbert is facing
OL,19,Fsevere brain damage.
