OL,3,CArena survivor hopes to protect
OL,4,Cdaughter from 'stalker man' conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheorist
OL,7,FBoth later became targets of author
OL,8,FRichard D Hall, who claimed the
OL,9,Fattack, in which Salman Abedi
OL,10,Fdetonated a homemade rucksack bomb in
OL,11,Fthe crowd of concert-goers, was faked
OL,12,Fby government agencies.
OL,14,FMr Hibbert said the five years of
OL,15,Fvideos and trolling by Mr Hall was
OL,16,F"mentally exhausting", leaving him
OL,17,Ffeeling unsafe, and scared to go to
OL,18,Fthe car on his own.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
