OL,3,CArena survivor hopes to protect
OL,4,Cdaughter from 'stalker man' conspiracy
OL,5,Ctheorist
OL,7,FHis daughter, Mr Hibbert said,
OL,8,Fdescribed the defendant as "the
OL,9,Fstalker man", while his wife Gabby
OL,10,Falso no longer feeling safe at home.
OL,12,FThe Hibberts are bringing a landmark
OL,13,Fdefamation and harassment case against
OL,14,FMr Hall, suing him over several videos
OL,15,Fand a book in which he has made claims
OL,16,Fthe bombing was a "hoax", as well as
OL,17,F"secretly filming" Eve and her mother
OL,18,Fat their house.
