OL,7,FDefending, lawyers for Mr Hall said
OL,8,Fhis actions were "pursued for the
OL,9,Fpurpose of preventing or detecting
OL,10,Fcrime" and that he has deleted the
OL,11,Ffootage from outside the home.
OL,13,FOn the opening day of the trial, at
OL,14,Fthe High Court in London, Mr Hall
OL,15,Farrived brandishing two books, in
OL,16,Fwhich he claims those killed and
OL,17,Finjured in the attack were part of a
OL,18,Fconspiracy to fool the public.
OL,26,@pD@ROUrD@FO]
