OL,7,FThe self-confessed conspiracy theorist
OL,8,Fclaims the Hibberts had been signed up
OL,9,Fas "crisis actors" with the victims
OL,10,Fagreeing to disappear, and many others
OL,11,Fclaiming they were injured.
OL,13,FOpening the case, Jonathan Price, for
OL,14,Fthe Hibberts, said the pair were some
OL,15,Fof the closest to Abedi when he
OL,16,Fdetonated the bomb and that the attack
OL,17,Fchanged Mr Hibbert's life "in every
OL,18,Fconceivable way".
OL,26,@yD@[OUzD@PO]
