OL,5,Ctheorist
OL,7,FMr Price added: "Martin, paralysed,
OL,8,Fsaw Eve lying next to him with a hole
OL,9,Fin her head and assumed he was
OL,10,Fwatching her die, unable to help.
OL,12,F"He saw others lying dead or injured
OL,13,Faround him."
OL,15,FHe continued: "Mr Hall does not accept
OL,16,Fany of this. His theory is that it is
OL,17,Fan elaborate hoax."
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@LO]wD@OOUyD@SO]
