OL,7,FThe defendant in his book and website
OL,8,Fhad claimed the fact Miss Hibbert did
OL,9,Fnot do interviews was "suspicious" and
OL,10,Fhe claimed that was evidence her
OL,11,Finjuries were fake.
OL,13,FThe court was told he had gone to her
OL,14,Fhome, and filmed the teenager coming
OL,15,Fout of her house in her wheelchair,
OL,16,Fand spoke to people in the street who
OL,17,Fdid not know she had been in the
OL,18,Fbombing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
