OL,5,Ctheorist
OL,7,FMr Hibbert had made a "positive
OL,8,Fchoice" to co-operate with the media
OL,9,Fconcerning the attack, the barrister
OL,10,Flater said.
OL,12,F"As such, it is Mr Hibbert who has
OL,13,Fcome to the 'harassment' and not the
OL,14,Fconverse."
OL,16,FThe court was later told that, while
OL,17,Fthere was one incident of filming,
OL,18,Fthis was from a public highway and the
OL,19,Ffootage was never published.
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@GO]tD@AOUvD@JO]
