OL,7,FMr Oakley continued: "It is submitted
OL,8,Fthat this single incident would not be
OL,9,Fsufficient to found an action."
OL,11,FThe trial before Mrs Justice Steyn is
OL,12,Fexpected to last four days with a
OL,13,Fdecision expected in writing at a
OL,14,Flater date.
